Feature: AI Learning Journey
  As a user
  I want to learn about AI concepts step by step
  So I can understand how AI works and apply it

  Scenario: Start AI lesson
    Given I am logged in
    When I begin my first AI lesson
    Then I see an introduction to AI

  Scenario: Complete an AI challenge
    Given I am learning about AI
    When I complete a challenge
    Then I earn points and unlock the next lesson
